I've been really looking forward to watching this special episode of 1, 2, 3 IVE. This is IVE's version of Impractical Jokers, but the more family friendly version, but it was still hilarious to watch. Annyeongz setting up the rest of IVE, who were flabbergasted when the chef asked them various personal questions through the earpiece. 😂 Their variety shows are getting more chaotic, but that's what I love about IVE. Neomu usgyeo. Annyeongz are enjoying the prank a bit too much. I've never seen both of them laughing this much, ever. Especially Wony. 1, 2, 3 Mafia. Ngl though, the food looks hella delicious. 
Oh so this video is linked with Ttala Hae Bol Rei as well? I am so looking forward to watching this week's episode of Ttala Hae Bol Rei to see her side of perspective.
